name: Global X Enhanced All-Equity Asset Allocation Covered Call ETF
longDescription: The fund investing, directly or indirectly, in exchange traded funds that provide exposure to a globally diversified portfolio of equity securities. To generate premiums, EQCL will be exposed to a dynamic covered call option writing program. EQCL seeks to provide a combination of a high level of income and longterm capital growth.
